# Rust
target/
# Cargo.lock IS tracked - DSPanel is a binary application (Tauri app),
# best practice per Cargo book: track Cargo.lock for reproducible builds
# and to ensure security patches on transitive deps propagate to all
# clones / CI runs.

# Node
node_modules/
dist/
.vite/
package-lock.json

# OS files
